Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.86,0:01:39.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:95867,99412}I heard that Graham's comet\Nwill soon be visible!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.62,0:01:41.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:99621,101414}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.62,0:01:44.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:101623,104500}I know Halley's comet,\Nbut not this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.70,0:01:49.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:104709,109464}It's the comet that passes\Nclose to Earth every 50 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.34,0:01:51.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:110340,111466}Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.67,0:01:55.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:111674,115970}I'm sure it's this Thursday\Nwhen it'll pass by Earth again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.59,0:01:59.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:116596,119682}How wonderful!\NThis Thursday, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.89,0:02:02.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:119891,122894}How romantic!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.60,0:02:10.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:125605,130943}But you can't see it with the naked\Neye. You have to go to an observatory.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.15,0:02:15.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:131152,135823}What would happen\Nif a comet crashed into Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.03,0:02:18.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:136032,138576}I guess we'd all be blown to bits.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.78,0:02:23.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:138785,143373}– Then what will you do, Ryoko?\N– Get my important things and run!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.58,0:02:25.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:143581,145958}– To where?\N– Your important things?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.16,0:02:29.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:146167,149712}– Let me think…\N– Important things, she says.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.92,0:02:33.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:149921,153716}– My parents, for sure!\N– Mine's my favorite fishing pole.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.92,0:02:38.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:153925,158304}My pillow! I can't sleep without it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.34,0:02:46.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:161349,166771}– You guys are a lost cause.\N– What about you, Sawatari?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.98,0:02:51.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:167980,171234}Let's run to the end of the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.27,0:02:58.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:175279,178658}No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.40,0:03:04.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:179409,184622}A COMET APPROACHES!\NTHE EARTH'S FINAL NIGHT??
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.03,0:03:06.54,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:185039,186541}You're all idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.74,0:03:11.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:186749,191671}A comet never leaves its orbit,\Nso it'll never crash into Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.87,0:03:15.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:191879,195550}I said "suppose"!\NDon't call me an idiot, you idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.80,0:03:17.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:195800,197719}You want a fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.92,0:03:23.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:197927,203307}So that's it! You don't have anything\Nimportant to take, so you're mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.59,0:03:27.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:203599,207562}What? You're wrong!\NI do too have something precious!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.14,0:03:30.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:208146,210982}– Then tell us!\N– You really want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.19,0:03:36.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:211190,216028}Are you two friends or enemies?\NMake up your mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.74,0:03:44.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:220742,224746}– Who wants to be friends with him?\N– Same here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.92,0:04:02.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:237925,242889}He didn't have time to tell me\Nwhat his important thing was.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.63,0:04:05.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:243639,245433}Make up my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.64,0:04:08.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:245641,248686}I'm not in love with her or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.93,0:04:12.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:249937,252356}I just don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.73,0:04:17.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:255735,257862}I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.07,0:04:22.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:258070,262408}We must let the American people\Nknow to prevent a tragedy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.61,0:04:25.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:262617,265828}But that will only cause a panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.03,0:04:29.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:266037,269791}– You're saying to keep quiet?\N– We only have a few minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.29,0:04:31.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:270291,271793}I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.58,0:04:35.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:272585,275254}Oh, welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.58,0:04:36.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:275588,276964}It's too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.17,0:04:39.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:277173,279884}It's too soon to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.09,0:04:44.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:280092,284305}– Mom, where's my snack?\N– There should be something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.51,0:04:46.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:284514,286224}Nope!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.43,0:04:52.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:286432,292021}Gosh! What are they watching anyway,\Nall cuddled up during the day?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.56,0:04:57.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:293564,297485}COMET COLLIDES!\NTHE LAST NIGHT ON EARTH: 1953 USA
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.08,0:05:15.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:313084,315044}It brings back memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.25,0:05:19.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:315253,319924}It sure did. This was the movie\Nwe saw on our first date.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.75,0:05:22.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:320758,322885}Genichiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.88,0:05:25.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:323886,325888}Eimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.06,0:05:33.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:331060,333896}I guess I'll go change.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.77,0:05:37.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:334772,337859}This is so embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.48,0:05:45.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:343489,345825}Sorry I'm late!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.61,0:05:49.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:347618,349370}What is it this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.57,0:05:54.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:349579,354292}Well, it's an incident that\Noccurred about an hour ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.58,0:05:56.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:354584,356752}I'm first!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.96,0:06:00.71,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:356961,360715}Ouch! You mustn't run around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.34,0:06:03.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:361340,363217}I'm sorry, Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.88,0:06:08.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:363885,368264}You're in the choir, aren't you?\NWhat's the big hurry?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.47,0:06:09.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:368472,369682}Truth is…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.18,0:06:15.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:373185,375146}Graham's comet?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.64,0:06:19.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:375646,379442}That's right, Sister.\NWe have to see that comet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.65,0:06:21.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:379650,381777}Akio's going to move away soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.98,0:06:26.11,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:381986,386115}That's why we all decided\Nto go see the comet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.32,0:06:29.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:386324,389702}– You can't see it with your naked eye.\N– I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.91,0:06:35.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:389911,395875}So I went to the observatory and asked\Nif we could use the telescope.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.08,0:06:38.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:396083,398794}At first they agreed, but then…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.21,0:06:44.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:401213,404258}No one's told me anything about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.71,0:06:47.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:404717,407386}But I talked to\Nthe director last week!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.59,0:06:52.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:407595,412475}Last week? That director was\Ntransferred to another observatory.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.89,0:06:53.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:412892,413893}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.06,0:06:56.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:414060,416979}Then let us talk to the new director!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.39,0:07:01.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:417396,421484}He's a busy man.\NYou're disrupting our work. Go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.77,0:07:03.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:421776,423486}– Oh, my.\N– It's not fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.69,0:07:09.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:423694,429408}We were looking forward to it.\NSo we came to pray for God's help.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.61,0:07:12.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:429617,432161}So we can get to see the comet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.70,0:07:20.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:437708,440503}Isn't there some other way, Seira?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.71,0:07:25.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:440711,445424}You can only see it with an\Nobservatory's astronomical telescope.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.88,0:07:27.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:445883,447927}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.17,0:07:32.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:448177,452139}Okay! Let St. Tail handle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.85,0:07:42.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:457853,462149}It looks like that Sawatari's\Nreally serious about Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.35,0:07:47.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:462358,467530}I wonder what got into him. He was\Nnever interested in girls before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.73,0:07:51.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:467738,471534}– What do you think, Asuka?\N– How would I know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.74,0:07:53.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:471742,473911}What a grouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.12,0:07:57.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:474120,477081}– Who cares?\N– Hey! The enemy is approaching!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.49,0:08:00.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:477498,480084}Prepare to fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.33,0:08:03.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:482336,483587}What…?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.79,0:08:06.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:483796,486590}What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.38,0:08:17.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:493389,497727}Rotten kids! How dare you\Nattack an innocent passerby?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.77,0:08:23.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:500771,503190}Adults are all liars!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.03,0:08:34.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:511032,514243}Hey, Asuka, looking good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.45,0:08:36.87,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:514452,516871}You can't hit me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.37,0:08:40.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:518372,520249}Great strategy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.67,0:08:48.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:526672,528215}"Dear Mr. Detective:
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.42,0:08:53.92,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:528424,533929}I will steal Graham's comet\Nthis coming Thursday. – St. Tail"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.68,0:08:57.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:534680,537433}– It's a challenge!\N– A challenge?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.64,0:09:00.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:537641,540352}Wow! Let me see!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.56,0:09:02.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:540561,542980}How's she gonna steal a comet?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.18,0:09:07.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:543189,547443}There's no way…\NSo that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.65,0:09:11.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:547651,551864}She's gonna steal\Nthe observatory's telescope!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.07,0:09:15.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:552073,555826}That's the only way to see\Nthe comet around here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.74,0:09:20.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:557745,560664}My theory's definitely right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.87,0:09:24.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:560873,564126}Never mind.\NYou're dripping all over the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.33,0:09:28.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:564335,568672}– But stealing it won't be easy.\N– I also agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.88,0:09:30.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:568881,570341}Did you hear that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.46,0:09:35.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:571467,575221}She'll think of a way!\NI'll be ready for you, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.42,0:09:38.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:575429,578432}How can he be so sure\Nbased on no facts?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.64,0:09:42.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:578641,582144}I don't know.\NIt must be love, love.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.18,0:09:49.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:585189,589360}It's a perfect night to present\Nthe comet to the children.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.61,0:09:52.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:589610,592738}Ruby, take care of things here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.40,0:09:59.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:596408,599787}No, Ruby! I have work to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.33,0:10:05.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:601330,605042}Oh, all right. Will you help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.00,0:10:09.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:606001,609213}Okay. But just this one time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.71,0:10:16.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:612716,616470}Oh, Lord, forgive me,\Nfor I use no gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.55,0:10:23.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:621559,623269}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.06,0:10:26.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:625062,626814}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.35,0:10:31.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:628357,631193}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.66,0:10:52.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:647668,652464}Meimi, hurry! Everyone will be\Nhere soon for choir practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.17,0:10:56.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:653174,656385}I know. You and Ruby take care\Nof the other things.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.67,0:11:00.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:656677,660306}The children will be happy for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.80,0:11:02.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:660806,662641}You can count on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.97,0:11:08.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:664977,668606}May the blessings of God be with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.09,0:11:47.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:703098,707228}Wow. This certainly is\Na magnificent telescope.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.44,0:11:53.65,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:712441,713651}Asuka Jr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.85,0:11:57.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:713859,717613}But why does she want a telescope?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.32,0:12:03.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:718322,723661}– It will go smoothly tonight.\N– Especially without those pesky kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.41,0:12:08.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:724411,728207}We can't let those kids ruin\Nsuch a great astronomical event.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.41,0:12:13.08,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:728415,733087}– How's it going?\N– Everything's going smoothly, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.29,0:12:14.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:733295,734421}Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.63,0:12:19.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:734630,739593}Asuka Jr., is St. Tail really\Ncoming to steal this telescope?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.96,0:12:21.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:739969,741595}I'm certain of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.09,0:12:26.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:742096,746016}You've got the right idea\Nexcept for the last detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.22,0:12:29.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:746225,749603}We'll leave you\Nto take care of St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.81,0:12:33.02,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:749812,753023}We don't want our research\Nhampered by a thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.60,0:12:35.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:753607,755150}Of all the nerve!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.35,0:12:40.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:755359,760155}The comet passes once every 50 years.\NIt's just as important to children.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.36,0:12:44.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:760364,764952}They want to keep it for themselves.\NGod will never forgive this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.45,0:12:47.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:765452,767121}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.24,0:12:49.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:768247,769957}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.16,0:12:52.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:770165,772042}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.21,0:13:00.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:778215,780843}– Where did they come from?\N– Who did this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.05,0:13:03.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:781051,783387}Stop this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.59,0:13:07.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:783595,787641}– No, stop!\N– I was wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.02,0:13:13.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:791020,793731}I know it's you, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.81,0:13:20.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:796817,800279}How's she gonna steal\Nthis huge thing anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.58,0:13:35.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:812583,815002}Well, that's all for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.21,0:13:40.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:815210,820674}And now, I have some sad news\Nfor all of you today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.09,0:13:44.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:821091,824053}Today is Akio's last practice…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.26,0:13:48.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:824261,828098}…since he will be leaving soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.89,0:13:54.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:832895,834688}– Take care.\N– Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.31,0:13:57.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:835314,837441}Too bad we couldn't see the comet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.64,0:14:00.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:837649,840778}– It can't be helped.\N– See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.52,0:14:05.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:841528,845908}Akio, I hope you never lose\Nyour bright outlook on life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.28,0:14:10.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:846283,850204}– I won't! Goodbye, Mother Superior!\N– Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.29,0:14:19.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:854291,859171}– Mother Superior, where is Seira?\N– She's not out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.92,0:14:27.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:864927,867805}Oh, but I am outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.84,0:14:32.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:869848,872851}Though this is a little embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.18,0:14:40.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:875187,880317}Hello, children! These balloons\Nare for you from the snowman!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.90,0:14:48.20,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:882903,888200}– This is a reward for being so good.\N– Gee, thanks, Mr. Snowman!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.82,0:14:52.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:888826,892704}There's one for everyone.\NHere you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.95,0:14:54.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:892955,894623}Wow! A snowman!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.62,0:14:59.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:897626,899128}Here you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.33,0:15:01.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:899336,901130}Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.59,0:15:14.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:909596,914059}Hey, Akio. There's something\Non your balloon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.72,0:15:21.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:917729,921483}Come to the observatory.\NI'll give you Graham's comet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.81,0:15:25.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:922818,925946}– Let's go!\N– Where are you kids going?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.23,0:15:28.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:926238,928449}We'll be right back, Mommy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.87,0:15:35.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:932870,935414}– What's this?\N– Get down here, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.78,0:15:38.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:935789,938375}If you don't, I'm going up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.83,0:15:43.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:940836,943839}I'll get you for sure today\Nand unmask you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.34,0:15:53.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:951346,953098}It's…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.18,0:15:57.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:954183,957102}…show…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.89,0:16:00.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:957895,960189}…time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.65,0:16:11.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:968655,971867}Sir! This is terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.45,0:16:15.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:972451,975537}– Look at the monitor!\N– What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.16,0:16:19.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:976163,979124}A part of the comet has broken off…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.33,0:16:22.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:979333,982044}…and is falling towards us\Nat great speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.25,0:16:24.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:982252,984671}That's ridiculous! Let me see!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.71,0:16:30.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:985714,990385}– Why didn't you see this before?\N– I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.22,0:16:35.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:991220,995849}A part of the comet. That's\Nsomething like a meteor, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.05,0:16:37.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:996058,997768}No, very far from it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.97,0:16:42.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:997976,1002147}It could make a huge hole!\NWe may not be safe here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.35,0:16:46.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1002356,1006818}– Let's get away!\N– Wait for me! Come back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.06,0:16:50.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1007069,1010030}Everyone's gone finally!\NNow's my chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.28,0:16:53.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1010280,1013534}Hey, you! Don't you move from there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.41,0:17:01.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1016411,1021416}Why aren't you running away?\NA part of the comet is heading here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.25,0:17:03.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1022251,1023585}So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.79,0:17:07.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1023794,1027422}So what? What could you\Nbe thinking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.96,0:17:10.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1027965,1030801}I'm gonna arrest you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.93,0:17:18.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1034930,1038308}My legs, I can't move them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.47,0:17:20.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1038475,1040310}Is there another reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.51,0:17:25.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1040519,1045274}Like what if you died, what's\Nthe most important thing you'd take?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.48,0:17:27.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1045482,1047317}Something important?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.52,0:17:30.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1047526,1050320}– Yes. Do you have something?\N– No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.52,0:17:34.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1050529,1054324}I can't think of anything\Nuntil I arrest you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.04,0:17:54.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1071049,1074428}Meimi, no! Get ahold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.81,0:18:06.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1084813,1086773}I'm sorry. It was an act.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.35,0:18:12.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1087357,1092279}Nothing's falling to Earth.\NI rigged the whole thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.94,0:18:14.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1092946,1094281}You what?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.48,0:18:17.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1094489,1097784}One! Two! Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.87,0:18:27.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1104875,1107210}COMET COLLIDES! THE LAST NIGHT\NON EARTH; THE END
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.46,0:18:29.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1107461,1109338}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.80,0:18:46.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1122809,1126063}Hey! Why did you do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.39,0:18:51.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1127397,1131443}Don't worry. I've recorded\Nthe correct data too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.65,0:18:55.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1131652,1135572}And could you let in\Nthe children waiting outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.94,0:18:57.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1135947,1137699}Outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.74,0:19:00.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1138742,1140577}Rats!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.78,0:19:02.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1140786,1142829}Come back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.54,0:19:08.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1145540,1148043}Boy, that was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.25,0:19:11.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1148251,1151046}But he wouldn't have said it\Nlike that…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.25,0:19:14.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1151254,1154257}…if he knew I was Meimi.\NI'm sure of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.18,0:19:23.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1161181,1163725}The children waiting outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.90,0:19:38.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1176905,1178990}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.49,0:19:46.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1184496,1186957}Wow, there it is! I see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.16,0:19:49.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1187165,1189459}– The comet!\N– It really has a tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.71,0:19:51.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1189710,1191586}Yeah, this is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.17,0:19:57.17,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1193171,1197175}– I wonder when we'll see it again?\N– In 50 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.42,0:20:00.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1197426,1200554}Then let's all come here\Nagain to look at it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.76,0:20:01.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1200762,1201805}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.01,0:20:05.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1202013,1205016}I just don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.22,0:20:09.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1205225,1209688}Why did St. Tail…?\NHey, what's this all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.89,0:20:13.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1209896,1213567}Thank you, sir.\NWe all prayed to God.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.31,0:20:17.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1214317,1217404}We asked Him to let us see the comet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.40,0:20:21.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1219406,1221992}Thank you, God!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.57,0:20:24.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1222576,1224619}God.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.49,0:20:30.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1226496,1230667}Look, falling stars!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.37,0:20:38.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1234379,1238008}Did you ask God for something?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.92,0:20:41.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1238925,1241136}– No.\N– Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.92,0:20:44.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1241928,1244848}Because my wish…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.05,0:20:47.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1245056,1247893}…is for God.
